snippet.title: India’s Chilling Warning To Pakistan After Ceasefire: ‘We Are Fully Ready And Alert’ | Full Briefing
snippet.description:
After the India-Pakistan ceasefire, top military officials-Commodore Raghu R Nair, Wing Commander Vyomika Singh, and Colonel Sofiya Qureshi-set the record straight. They exposed Pakistan’s false claims about S-400, BrahMos, and airfield damage, reaffirmed India’s secular values, and clarified that only terrorist targets were hit. India’s armed forces remain vigilant and ready for any threat, even as both nations halt hostilities on land, sea, and air. Watch the full briefing.

pt-BR.description:

hi.description:
भारत-पाकिस्तान युद्ध विराम के बाद, शीर्ष सैन्य अधिकारियों-कमोडोर रघु आर नायर, विंग कमांडर व्योमिका सिंह और कर्नल सोफिया कुरैशी ने सच्चाई सामने रखी। उन्होंने एस-400, ब्रह्मोस और एयरफील्ड क्षति के बारे में पाकिस्तान के झूठे दावों को उजागर किया, भारत के धर्मनिरपेक्ष मूल्यों की पुष्टि की और स्पष्ट किया कि केवल आतंकवादी ठिकानों को ही निशाना बनाया गया। भारत के सशस्त्र बल सतर्क हैं और किसी भी खतरे के लिए तैयार हैं, भले ही दोनों देश जमीन, समुद्र और हवा में शत्रुता को रोक रहे हों। पूरी ब्रीफिंग देखें।

de-DE.title: Indiens eindringliche Warnung an Pakistan nach dem Waffenstillstand: „Wir sind völlig bereit und ...
de-DE.description:
Nach dem Waffenstillstand zwischen Indien und Pakistan stellten hochrangige Militärs – Kommodore Raghu R. Nair, Geschwaderkommandeur Vyomika Singh und Oberst Sofiya Qureshi – die Dinge richtig. Sie deckten Pakistans falsche Behauptungen über S-400, BrahMos und Schäden an Flugplätzen auf, bekräftigten Indiens säkulare Werte und stellten klar, dass ausschließlich terroristische Ziele getroffen wurden. Indiens Streitkräfte bleiben wachsam und bereit für jede Bedrohung, auch wenn beide Nationen die Feindseligkeiten zu Land, zu Wasser und in der Luft einstellen. ja.title: 停戦後、インドがパキスタンに厳しい警告：「我々は万全の準備と警戒態勢を整えている」 | 完全版
ja.description:
インドとパキスタンの停戦後、ラグー・R・ナイル准将、ヴィオミカ・シン空軍中佐、ソフィヤ・クレシ大佐といった軍高官が事実関係を明らかにしました。彼らは、S-400、ブラモス、そして飛行場の被害に関するパキスタンの虚偽の主張を暴露し、インドの世俗的価値観を再確認し、攻撃を受けたのはテロリストの標的のみであることを明確にしました。両国が陸海空における敵対行為を停止しているにもかかわらず、インド軍は警戒を怠らず、あらゆる脅威に備えています。ブリーフィングの全編をご覧ください。

it.title: L'agghiacciante avvertimento dell'India al Pakistan dopo il cessate il fuoco: "Siamo pienamente p...
it.description:
Dopo il cessate il fuoco tra India e Pakistan, alti ufficiali militari – il Commodoro Raghu R. Nair, il Comandante di Squadriglia Vyomika Singh e il Colonnello Sofiya Qureshi – hanno chiarito le cose. Hanno smascherato le false affermazioni del Pakistan su S-400, BrahMos e danni agli aeroporti, hanno ribadito i valori laici dell'India e hanno chiarito che sono stati colpiti solo obiettivi terroristici. Le forze armate indiane rimangono vigili e pronte a qualsiasi minaccia, anche se entrambe le nazioni hanno interrotto le ostilità via terra, mare e aria. Guarda il briefing completo.

snippet.title: Dream VS Daquavis $100,000 Minecraft Skills Duel

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

Daquavis:  @DaquavisMC

hi.title: ड्रीम बनाम डेक्विस $100,000 Minecraft कौशल द्वंद्वयुद्ध
hi.description:
ड्रीम बनाम डेक्वाविस $100,000 Minecraft कौशल द्वंद्वयुद्ध। यह PvP द्वंद्वयुद्ध का अनुवर्ती है। यह पागलपन था।

मेरे सोशल मीडिया को फॉलो करें:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic

डेक्वाविस: @DaquavisMC

यह $100,000 के लिए हमारे द्वंद्वयुद्ध में दूसरी चुनौती है। हम Minecraft के नवीनतम संस्करण पर 10 अलग-अलग Minecraft कौशलों में द्वंद्वयुद्ध कर रहे हैं। यदि ड्रीम यह मैच जीतता है, तो वह कुल मिलाकर 2 - 0 से जीतता है, और $100,000 जीतता है। यदि डेक्वाविस यह मैच जीतता है, तो यह 1 - 1 से बराबर हो जाएगा, और टाई ब्रेकर के रूप में मैनहंट होगा।

हमारे लिए चुनौतियों की स्थापना करने के लिए BadBoyHalo को धन्यवाद, ताकि हम एक निष्पक्ष मैच खेल सकें। कमेंट्री करने के लिए Technodad को धन्यवाद। मानचित्र बनाने में मदद करने के लिए कार्डीक्राफ्ट को धन्यवाद।

पहला भाग: https://youtu.be/hlTGjc7Gn04

सभी गाने और संगीत ड्रीम और पार्कर मकानी द्वारा इस वीडियो के लिए एक साउंड ट्रैक के रूप में कस्टम निर्मित किए गए हैं।

snippet.title: Prema Velluva - Video Song | HIT 3 | Nani | Sailesh Kolanu | Srinidhi Shetty | Mickey J Meyer
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe 👉 https://bit.ly/Saregama_Telugu

Presenting the video song of ''Prema Velluva'' from ''HIT 3'' starring Nani and Srinidhi Shetty. Directed by Dr. Sailesh Kolanu. Music Composed by Mickey J Meyer. Sung by Sid Sriram and Nutana Mohan. 

Song Credits:
Singers: Sid Sriram, Nutana Mohan
Lyrics: Krishna Kanth
Music: Mickey J Meyer
Choreography: Vishwa Raghu
Costume Designer: Nani Kamarsu
Stills: Sridhar Chadalawada
Keyboards: Mickey J Meyer
Rhythm: Venkatesh Patvari
Bass: Neil
Song Mixed by: Mickey J Meyer
Song Mastered by: Darren Vermaas (NY)
Music Recording Studio: Inspire Studio (California, Hyderabad)

Cast & Crew Details:
Starring 'Natural Star' as 'Arjun Sarkaar'.
Writer & Director : Dr. Sailesh Kolanu
Producer : Prashanti Tipirneni
Banners : Wall Poster Cinema & Unanimous Productions
Music : Mickey J Meyer
Cinematography : Sanu John Varghese
Editor : Karthika Srinivas R
Production Designer : Sri Nagendra Tangala
Executive Producer : S Venkatratnam (Venkat)
Sound design : Sync Cinema
PRO : Vamsi Shekar
Marketing : First Show
Publicity Designs : Aesthetic Kunjamma

Lyrics:

Dhuke naapai ila 
Ivvale ye ye 
Prema velluvaa

Pallavi 1:
Pagale naa vaipuki nadiche kalavaa 
Paduthuu yegire alavaa
Manase ninu chudani okate godava 
Kanule ipude chadhivaa
Venta vacchave Vembadinchaave 
Oopiralle maarave nede neeve
Nammi theerale kala kaadhe 
Peruke nenunnale praanam neeve
Yevarevarani vethikina Kanulaki thanu dhorikenaa 
Marichaanika dheninainaa nee valana
 
Pallavi 2:
Telusa tholisaariga 
Manase gelichaa 
Yepudu yedhute nilichaa
Kopam marichaanugaa Idi nee mahimaa?
Nijame nuvu naa sagamaa?

Chorus:
Prema Velluvaa…
Prema Uppenaa…
Prema Sandhadi…

Prema Velluvaa…
Prema Uppenaa…
Prema Sandhadi…

Charanam:
Ato ito yetainaa
Aduge jarige mela mellagaa Marintha 
okatokatiga cherenaa 
Manalo maname kalise vidhama
Geetha geesane vechi choosane
Ninnu minchi naakinka thodantu dhorukunaa
Aapalenule aagalenule Choopalenule cheppalenule
Dhaachalenu neninkaa naalo preema
Yevarevarani vethikina Kanulaki thanu dhorikena 
Marichaanika dheninainaa nee valana

Chorus:
Prema Velluvaa…
Prema Uppenaa…
Prema Sandhadi…

Prema Velluvaa…
Prema Uppenaa…
Prema Sandhadi…

snippet.title: बेटी की सफलता पर माता-पिता का गर्व, सुनिए Wing Commander Vyomika Singh के अनसुने किस्से
snippet.description:
विंग कमांडर व्योमिका सिंह भारतीय वायुसेना की एक प्रतिष्ठित अधिकारी और आज पूरे देश के लिए प्रेरणास्रोत बन चुकी हैं. उनके माता-पिता, आर.एस. नीम और करुणा सिंह ने गुड न्यूज़ टुडे के संजय शर्मा के साथ एक विशेष बातचीत में व्योमिका के बचपन की शरारतों, जैसे पाइप से उतरना, से लेकर वायुसेना में उनके चयन तक के सफर को साझा किया. उन्होंने बताया कि कैसे व्योमिका ने चुपचाप वायुसेना के लिए आवेदन किया और देहरादून में प्रशिक्षण के लिए 700 में से अकेली लड़की के तौर पर चुनी गईं. उनकी मां ने लड़कियों को संदेश दिया, "एक लड़की और लड़के में कोई अंतर नहीं है" और अपने सपनों को साकार करने का आग्रह किया. व्योमिका सिंह ने भारत-पाकिस्तान तनाव के दौरान भी राष्ट्र को महत्वपूर्ण जानकारी दी थी.

snippet.description:
All Research References & Links for further read - https://docs.google.com/document/d/185u16NexzVqUwePbh5YUlnsiAxk3WcieOb5tFQ5UgRE/edit?usp=sharing

Like our work, are CRAZY about Science & want to JOIN us? Please fill the applicable form and we will get in touch with you! (Interns can also apply)

Join as a Science Writer/Researcher/ Experiment Engineer  → https://forms.gle/NmemSnhfDkdaPEAt5

Join as a Geopolitical, History, Political Science Writer  → https://forms.gle/hKCwEETKhfiUHY7F7

Perks of joining us : 

1. Massive social impact on millions of minds through your work.
2. Being a part of one of the Largest YouTube Media Companies with 6 thriving YT Channels into varied genres, learn the ins and outs of social media, the new age skill.
3. A safe work environment of like-minded vision-sharing people.
4. Salary compensation: Better than industry standards while doing what you love.

Connect over Instagram → https://instagram.com/gauravzthakur

Also, for News & Current Affair analysis, Geopolitics/Politics related content or to sharpen your General Knowledge in general, check out my 2nd channel Gaurav Thakur : https://www.youtube.com/@GauravThakur-GSF
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Has an Indian-origin scientist finally discovered alien life? Dr. Nikku Madhusudhan, an IIT Varanasi graduate and astrophysicist at Cambridge University, along with his team, has identified an exoplanet — K2-18b — that may hold strong potential for life. News channels are buzzing with claims that this might be the breakthrough scientists like Stephen Hawking and even Nikola Tesla once dreamed of. But isn’t it strange how we hear such headlines almost every year? From Proxima Centauri B and the TRAPPIST-1 system, to LHS 1140b and the so-called “super-Earth” Kepler-452B — each time we're told alien life is finally found. And yet, the undeniable truth remains: there’s no confirmed evidence of alien life to date. So, is Dr. Madhusudhan’s discovery another media-fueled hype? Or has something genuinely groundbreaking happened this time? Let’s dig into what really makes K2-18b different — and whether it truly brings us closer to answering the age-old question: Are we alone?

snippet.title: The Conjuring: Last Rites | Official Teaser
snippet.description:
Last Case. Last Rites. #TheConjuring: Last Rites - Only in Theaters September 5.

From New Line Cinema comes the ninth entry in the more than $2 billion theatrical Conjuring universe, The Conjuring: Last Rites, directed by franchise veteran Michael Chaves and produced by franchise architects James Wan and Peter Safran.

The Conjuring: Last Rites delivers another thrilling chapter of the iconic Conjuring cinematic universe, based on real events. Vera Farmiga and Patrick Wilson reunite for one last case as renowned, real-life paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren in a powerful and spine-chilling addition to the global box office-breaking franchise.

Farmiga and Wilson star alongside Mia Tomlinson and Ben Hardy, who portray Ed and Lorraine’s daughter Judy Warren and her boyfriend, Tony Spera, as well as Steve Coulter returning as Father Gordon, Rebecca Calder, Elliot Cowan, Kíla Lord Cassidy, Beau Gadsdon, John Brotherton and Shannon Kook.

Chaves directs from a screenplay by Ian Goldberg & Richard Naing and David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, story by David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick & James Wan, based on characters created by Chad Hayes & Carey W. Hayes. 

The executive producers are Michael Clear, Judson Scott, Natalia Safran, John Rickard, Hans Ritter and David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick. Chaves is joined behind the camera by his creative team, including director of photography Eli Born, production designer John Frankish, editors Elliot Greenberg and Gregory Plotkin, visual effects supervisor Scott Edelstein, visual effects producer Eric Bruneau and costume designer Graham Churchyard, with casting by Rose Wicksteed and Sophie Kingston-Smith. 

The music supervisor is Ian Broucek and the music is by composer Benjamin Wallfisch. New Line Cinema Presents A Safran Company / An Atomic Monster Production, The Conjuring: Last Rites. The film will be released worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and will be only in theaters and IMAX® in North America on September 5, 2025, and internationally beginning 3 September 2025.

snippet.title: Grand Theft Auto VI Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Vice City, USA.

Jason and Lucia have always known the deck is stacked against them. But when an easy score goes wrong, they find themselves on the darkest side of the sunniest place in America, in the middle of a criminal conspiracy stretching across the state of Leonida — forced to rely on each other more than ever if they want to make it out alive. 

Explore Vice City and beyond at https://www.rockstargames.com/VI

This trailer was captured entirely in-game from a PlayStation 5, comprised of equal parts gameplay and cutscenes.

Song: Hot Together
Artist: The Pointer Sisters
Written by Sharon Robinson
Published by Universal Music Corp. on behalf of itself, Buchu Music and Robinhill Music (ASCAP)

snippet.title: Vala the Intro | Jagathy Sreekumar | Arun Chandu | Sankar Sharma | The Imbachi
snippet.description:
Presenting the Official Special Intro of Vala, Directed by Arun chandu starring Jagathy Sreekumar, Gokul Suresh, Basil Joseph, Vineeth Sreenivasan, Anarkali Marikar, Aju Varghese, KB Ganesh Kumar, Giju John, John Kaippalill, Bhagat Manuel, Aadi, produced by Turtle Vine Productions in Association with Letters Entertainment.!

Director: Arun Chandu
Story Screenplay Dialogues: Tyler Durden, Arun Chandu
Producer: Turtle Vine Productions in Association with Letters Entertainment
Distribution: Funtastic Films Release
Director Of Photography (Promo) : Guru Prasad MG, Surjith S Pai.
Editor: Ceejay Achu
Music: Sankar Sharma
Rap & Lyrics: The Imbachi
Art: Reneesh Regi
Creative Director: Vineesh Nakulan
Vfx: Meraki
Chief Associate Director (Promo): Nithin Michael 
Production Controller (Promo ): Sajeev Chandiroor
Production Executive: Antony Kuttampuzha
Production Manager: Eldho John
Production Officials: Ananthakrishnan Sreekumar, Saneesh Chandiroor
Directors Team: Arun Lal, Shri Hari, Ajay Krishnan Vijayan
Makeup: Ronex Savior
Costumes: Bucy Baby John
Sound Design: Sidharthan and Sankaran
Sound Mix: Vishnu Sujathan
Stills: Rakesh Anand
Designs: hal9000
Pro: Athira Diljith, Hains
Visual Promotions : Snakeplant LLP

Lyrics:

Intro - 
Asato Ma Sadgamaya, Tamaso Ma Jyotirgamaya, Mrityor Ma Amritamgamaya
Verse 1 - 
Now, the world’s burning down, see?
Truth in these eyes looking grey, I call it icy, 
War cries till the night, see?
New age killers going around looking feisty,
Do you feel the pain? Do you see the rage? 
Everything reverse, life is just a maze, Caught up in the dirt…
Aye, aye, Captain
Verse 2 - 
Feeling like my world’s simulated, my days feeling faded, 
Now, the dead, they walk around everyday like they made it, 
I said it, it’s parasitic, I get it, it’s all embedded, 
We’re living, we’re going at it, 
We’re riling another riot, get it?
Bridge - 
Now you see the hope, lighting up the throne,
We’re gonna make it out, we’re gonna make it know,
Bringing you the fight, find me in my zone, 
This is gonna be my calling, I said I’m not alone, 
Everyday we’re going all in, now, we’re gonna make it known 
Outro - 
Asato Ma Sadgamaya, Tamaso Ma Jyotirgamaya, Mrityor Ma Amritamgamaya

snippet.title: सूजी मूंगदाल फरा नाश्ते के लिए परफेक्ट स्वाद सेहत सादगी नो फ्राई नो झंझट । Steamed Sooji Fara recipe
snippet.description:
तला-भुना छोड़िए, अब खाइए स्टीम्ड और हेल्दी फरे, बिना झंझट वाला पौष्टिक नाश्ता,पारंपरिक स्वाद, बनाने में एकदम आसान, Sooji Fara Recipe – A Nutritious Start to Your Day,Low-Oil Breakfast – Sooji Fara with Protein-Rich Stuffing
#fara #breakfast #nashtha

Ingredients for Suji Moong Dal Fare
नमक - Salt - 3/4 tsp
तेल - Oil - 1 tbsp
सूजी - Semolina - 1 cup (180 grams)

For Stuffing
मूंग धुली दाल - Moong dhuli dal - 1/2 cup (100 grams)
नमक - Salt - 1/4 tsp
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 tsp, grated
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1/2 tsp, chopped
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1/2 tsp
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
लाल मिर्च पाउडर - Red chilli powder - 1/4 tsp
अमचूर पाउडर - Dry mango powder - 1/4 tsp
गरम मसाला - Garam masala - 1/4 tsp
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/2 tsp, crushed
हींग - Asafoetida - 1/2 pinch

snippet.description:

Biryani Gravy

Today I am going to share you Hyderabadi special chicken dum biryani recipe in a simple & Quick Way.Hyderabadi Chicken Dum Biryani is a world famous aromatic and flavorful rice dish that originated in the royal kitchens of the Nizams of Hyderabad. It is a classic example of the rich Mughlai and Andhra culinary fusion. This biryani is prepared using the traditional dum method, where marinated chicken is layered with partially cooked basmati rice, fragrant spices, caramelized onions, mint, and saffron-infused milk, then sealed and slow-cooked in its own steam.But in this recipe we are mixing the blends in simple  homestyle method with traditional Hyderabadi chicken biryani aroma & taste.Do try this tasty chicken dum biryani at home and leave your valuable feedback in comment section🤗.If you like this video please do like share & subscribe👍

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.description:
When we decided to release ´Story of a Bird´, there was one thing we knew for sure. We wanted it to be about more than just us. So we reached out to you. To share your creative moments, and be a part of the story. 

The official music video is here. And it´s made with your voices, your ideas. 
Hope you like it! 

#createforchange

- Alan

//////////////// 

Lyrics:

Verse 1
Khulli aakhoon se
WITH MY EYES OPEN
Maine jo sapna dekha hai
THE DREAM I'VE SEEN
Wo kitna sach hua hai
SO MUCH HAS IT COME TRUE
kitna adhoora reh gaya hai
SO MUCH HAS STAYED UNFULFILLED
jaane kahaan manzil
WHERE DO I GO
jaane kahaan mera pata hai
WHERE'S MY DESTINATION
kabhi na pucha khud se abtak kitna safar taye hua hai?
NEVER ASKED MYSELF HOW FAR WE'VE COME

Pre-Chorus
ab dekhna hai
WE SHALL SEE NOW
hawa mein jaise panchhi udhta hai
HOW THE BIRD SOARS THROUGH THE SKY
hawa se maano ladhne chal padha hai
FIGHTING THE WINDS
paa hi lega asmaan
THE SKY IS YOURS
ab dekhna hai
WE SHALL SEE NOW
aandhiyon se jo utha dhua hai
SMOKE IS RISING FROM THE STORM
vo dhue se paar ho gaya to
CROSS THE STORM 
paa hi lega ye jahaan
AND THE WORLD IS YOURS

Verse 2
vo fikar chhod chuka hai
HE'S DOESN'T CARE NOW
khud se pehli baar mila hai
HE'S MET HIMSELF NOW
khud se pehla pyaar hua hai
HE LOVES HIMSELF NOW
vapas na aayega
HE'S NOT COMING BACK
vo pannchhi mujhsa laga to
THE BIRD FEELS LIKE ΜΕ
maine ek kahaani likhi
I WROTE A STORY
vo khud se to keh na sakega
HE'LL NEVER SAY THIS TO HIMSELF
to apni zubaani likhi
SO I WROTE MY HEART OUT

Pre-Chorus
ab dekhna hai
WE SHALL SEE NOW
hawa mein jaise panchhi udhta hai
HOW THE BIRD SOARS THROUGH THE SKY
hawa se maano ladhne chal padha hai
FIGHTING THE WINDS
paa hi lega asmaan
THE SKY IS YOURS
ab dekhna hai
WE SHALL SEE NOW
aandhiyon se jo utha dhua hai
vo dhue se paar ho gaya to
CROSS THE DUST FROM THE STORM
paa hi lega ye jahaan
AND THE WORLD IS YOURS

snippet.title: This One is for the Farmers | Dreamz Unlimited | MPACS
snippet.description: Multipurpose Primary Agricultural Cooperative Societies (MPACS) are grassroots-level cooperative institutions in rural India that offer a wide range of services to farmers and rural communities. Unlike traditional Primary Agricultural Credit Societies (PACS), which mainly provide short-term agricultural credit, MPACS function as integrated rural support centers. They offer credit facilities, supply essential farm inputs like seeds, fertilizers, and pesticides, provide storage solutions, rent out farm equipment, and assist in the procurement and marketing of agricultural produce. In some cases, they also extend non-farm credit and facilitate access to banking and insurance services. MPACS are owned and managed by their local members, mainly farmers, and operate under the State Cooperative Societies Acts as part of the three-tier cooperative credit structure that includes District Central Cooperative Banks and State Cooperative Banks. These societies play a vital role in rural development by empowering small and marginal farmers, promoting financial inclusion, and encouraging self-reliance in agriculture. Despite facing challenges like poor management, limited modernization, and financial constraints, MPACS continue to be a powerful tool for strengthening the rural economy.
